{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2019-08-01--react-hlm-development/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://unearned-in.com","disqus":"gatsby-typescript"}},"post":{"html":"<h1 id=\"react-hlm\"><a href=\"#react-hlm\" aria-label=\"react hlm permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>react-hlm</h1>\n<p>react-hlmというコンポーネントを開発しました。<br>\nReactでこんな感じに文字を表示できます。<br>\n<img src=\"/369efe55794bd7aa551508872d27c22f/react-hlm.gif\"><br>\nリポジトリ : <a href=\"https://github.com/Y0KUDA/react-hlm\">https://github.com/Y0KUDA/react-hlm</a><br>\nデモページ : <a href=\"https://y0kuda.github.io/react-hlm/index.html\">https://y0kuda.github.io/react-hlm/index.html</a><br>\nNPM : <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-hlm\">https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-hlm</a>  </p>\n<p>名前の由来はタイトルの通りホットラインマイアミです。<br>\n雰囲気が好きなので、Reactでそれっぽいバナーやテキストを目指しました。<br>\n<img src=\"/254de5d3e0da52e3cf874aa6463ce984/hotlinemiami_banner.gif\"><br>\n<img src=\"/9139e77a5d2e6617da088322d49e95d2/hotlinemiami_text.gif\">    </p>\n<h1 id=\"使い方\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E3%81%84%E6%96%B9\" aria-label=\"使い方 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使い方</h1>\n<p>npmで公開しているので<code class=\"language-text\">npm</code>や<code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code>で<code class=\"language-text\">react-hlm</code>をインストールすれば使えます。<br>\nこんな感じのコードで簡単にバナーを出せます。  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">HLM</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Banner text<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sample\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>詳しくはリポジトリを参照してください。  </p>\n<p>種類も色々作りました。<br>\n<img src=\"/13795f8f2bd531a784d258dbe7239658/samples.gif\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"技術的な話\"><a href=\"#%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%9A%84%E3%81%AA%E8%A9%B1\" aria-label=\"技術的な話 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>技術的な話</h1>\n<h2 id=\"立体に表示する方法\"><a href=\"#%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E3%81%AB%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"立体に表示する方法 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>立体に表示する方法</h2>\n<p>エレメントの高さを0にすることで、同じ場所に複数のテキストを表示することができます。<br>\n少しずつずらして表示することで3Dっぽく表示してます。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">keys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">layer</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span>  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div  key<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token string\">\"_key\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n                style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">assign</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>top<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">calc(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>vecY<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>distance<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">px - </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>elementHeight<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">px )</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      left<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>vecX<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>distance<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      position<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"relative\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      height<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//　高さが0</span>\n                                      color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">acid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>time<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>colorSpeed<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      zIndex<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>layer<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"正しい領域を設定する方法\"><a href=\"#%E6%AD%A3%E3%81%97%E3%81%84%E9%A0%98%E5%9F%9F%E3%82%92%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"正しい領域を設定する方法 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>正しい領域を設定する方法</h2>\n<p>立体表示をするためにエレメントの高さを0にしてしまっているので、そのままだと領域がおかしくなってしまいます。<br>\n今回は同じテキストのエレメントを非表示で作成し、その領域内にずらして入れ込むことで領域を設定しています。  </p>\n<p>まず、以下のコードで何も表示しない領域を作成します。  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>visibility<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hidden\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> ref<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>ref<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token comment\">// visibility:\"hidden\" にすると表示されない。</span>\n                                              <span class=\"token comment\">// ref={ref} とすると、refからエレメントを参照できる。</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>すると、こんな感じの領域が発生します。<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 354px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/02da4909b6ccb5b8803245ee124a944e/1a1ab/box-shift.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.05084745762711%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"box shift\"\n        title=\"box shift\"\n        src=\"/static/02da4909b6ccb5b8803245ee124a944e/1a1ab/box-shift.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/02da4909b6ccb5b8803245ee124a944e/acf4b/box-shift.png 173w,\n/static/02da4909b6ccb5b8803245ee124a944e/fc834/box-shift.png 345w,\n/static/02da4909b6ccb5b8803245ee124a944e/1a1ab/box-shift.png 354w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>次に、以下のコードでエレメントの高さを取得します。  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\">    <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">setElementHeight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ref<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>offsetHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// refからエレメントの高さを取得し、設定。</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'resize'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token function\">setElementHeight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ref<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>offsetHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ウインドウがリサイズされたときに高さが更新されるようにイベントを設定。</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">updateTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> t <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">clearInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>最後に、取得した高さ分を差し引いて表示するようにします。  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">keys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">layer</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span>  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div  key<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token string\">\"_key\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n                style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">assign</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>top<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">calc(</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>vecY<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>distance<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">px - </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>elementHeight<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">px )</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// - ${elementHeight}px で必要な高さを差し引く。</span>\n                                      left<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>vecX<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>distance<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      position<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"relative\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      height<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">acid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>time<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>colorSpeed<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>layer<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token number\">0.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                                      zIndex<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>layer<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>いい感じに収まりました。<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 329px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d1873c26cb5afb4f7f5f15ee87037597/fb156/box.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.3677811550152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"box\"\n        title=\"box\"\n        src=\"/static/d1873c26cb5afb4f7f5f15ee87037597/fb156/box.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d1873c26cb5afb4f7f5f15ee87037597/acf4b/box.png 173w,\n/static/d1873c26cb5afb4f7f5f15ee87037597/fb156/box.png 329w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n 